{"tid":1677901,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作咗首歌送別蓋清","createTime":"2019-10-27T11:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T13:03:58.000Z","uid":154406,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8df2f640a977953124d613281119d755ca37676","tid":1677901,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"哪裡有蓋清告訴我 能不能把你的膠Po還給我<br />\n為什麼你這麼安靜 所有的Po都跑到了高登<br />\n<br />\n看不見妳的po我怎麼笑得出 妳的文字這麼近我卻看不到<br />\n沒有蓋清 波台還是會在 沒有膠po 我也能自己開<br />\n<br />\n蓋清離開 我知道很簡單 蓋清瀨屎 是我們的笑話<br />\n就算派膠 但能不能別離開這波台 你走了之後才明白<br />\n<br />\n挽留蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902a453ba67995e3390179dccd1b6a787511beaf","tid":1677901,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceb57617a6e7418e342155f95df76b856a8f2ab","tid":1677901,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1156a1bdc4168f54c2f8c5e63f5b5b3e18e041","tid":1677901,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"逆sir愛蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e67d13bf91ac64cf5468045ba9b419f766baf61","tid":1677901,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1156a1bdc4168f54c2f8c5e63f5b5b3e18e041","tid":1677901,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"逆sir愛蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"你不愛嗎"},{